{"tid":1487733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［真正民主］少數服從多數 但係多數要尊重少數","createTime":"2019-08-19T11:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T06:41:32.000Z","uid":287032,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f3f4b672f071cbc8a3b364e7880e72b6afb77d4c","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:34:08.000Z","msg":"成日見到tg 連登開投票post<br />\n一見到過半數或者超過70%<br />\n就即刻話已有共識 甚至屌少數係鬼<br />\n其實咁講係好撚唔尊重少數個班手足<br />\n而好多時最前線最勇武既只得5-10%<br />\n<br />\n170萬人10%都講緊17萬人啦<br />\n30%就係50幾萬人<br />\n唔通全部係鬼咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以請大家唔好成日用投票結果黎欺壓手足<br />\n咁先係真正不分化 不割蓆"},{"pid":"f92d680c32b44a3d32fd9066d51d406be5ad87e7","tid":1487733,"uid":222238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:36:30.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家無論如何都係同一條船"},{"pid":"3e4b4e08bc23e27ddc062c7e3a6ff867eb3a8efe","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"931c4ecf8ae005bbf45a8893bab24c129b67f950","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T11:39:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52aac2c2b6ed351ae4bc397e31aae8e9ff18e0a6","tid":1487733,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"尊重 包容"},{"pid":"a562407b1f8b38e5d4a55fb9df29fdfb545fa4f0","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T12:37:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c65b69cb7a2e0481c16858a4dc1af1d3e7fae09e","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T15:10:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"594d50fdb43b6893b9f16e93eea84b0678d79caf","tid":1487733,"uid":287032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}